value.value: Hello!
Yo, what's good?
Been a while, huh?
Totally, been swamped with work and family stuff.
Everything okay? Need any help?
Moved around a lot lately, like 3 times in 5 months.
That's wild!  What's the story?
Landed a gig at a tech firm, first move was for that.
But they shifted me to another city after just a month.
Total hassle, we had just settled the kids and everything.
So we packed up and moved again.
Insane, right?
Then the pandemic hit, and they switched us to remote work right after we moved.
So we moved back to our original spot since everything was set up there.
Man, thats rough. Sorry you went through all that!
Appreciate it! Great to catch up.
For sure. Lets do a virtual coffee next week!
:) Sounds good! Talk next week!
Catch ya later!
Yo, you free now? Wanna do that virtual coffee today? :)
Hey there!
Yeah, lets do it! Can I call you in 10 minutes?
Perfect! Call me in 10.
